                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8750" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0269</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1159 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">责任先行，绿启未来：民族涂料富思特的社会责任践行之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Responsibility first, greening future: the way to practice social responsibility of national Coatings Fusite</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">孙晶慧，王树斌，李芝芳，侯博文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安邮电大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">富思特新材料科技发展有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业社会责任；可持续发展；全方位社会责任管理；绿色转型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Corporate Social Responsibility;Sustainable development;All-round social responsibility management;Green transformation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着全球气候显著变化，人类经济社会发展与生态系统遭遇不容忽视的威胁，可持续发展引起涂料行业高度关注。企业社会责任是可持续发展语境下企业统筹经济效益、社会效益和环境效益融合发展的理论实践。本案例结合富思特新材料科技发展股份有限公司的社会责任实践，立足公司发展历程，描述了富思特“质量至上，诚信经营”的履责起点，“抢抓机遇，并购红狮”的履责担当，以及“环保理念，生根发芽”的履责进路，重点介绍了其在生产运营中全方位社会责任管理的具体表现，进一步展现了社会责任与提升可持续发展能力的相互关系。通过案例分析，帮助学生理解企业社会责任和可持续发展的理论与相关关系，激发学生的爱国情怀和担当精神，也为其他涂料企业通过履行社会责任实现绿色转型提供重要启示。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With significant changes in the global climate, human economic and social development and the ecosystem have encountered threats that cannot be ignored, and sustainable development has attracted great attention from the coating industry. Corporate social responsibility is the theory and practice of integrating economic benefit, social benefit and environmental benefit under the context of sustainable development. This case combines the social responsibility practice of Fusite New Material Technology Development Co., LTD., based on the company&#39;s development history, describes the starting point of Fusite&#39;s performance of &quot;quality first, integrity management&quot;, the performance responsibility of &quot;seizing opportunities, acquiring Red Lion&quot;, and the performance path of &quot;environmental protection concept, root and sprout&quot;. This paper focuses on the specific performance of all-round social responsibility management in production and operation, and further demonstrates the interrelationship between social responsibility and enhancing sustainable development ability. Through case analysis, it helps students understand the theoretical exposition and correlation between corporate social responsibility and sustainable development, stimulates students&#39; patriotic feelings and sense of responsibility, and also provides important inspiration for other paint enterprises to realize green transformation through fulfilling social responsibility.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会责任》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业社会责任的内涵；企业社会责任的驱动因素；利益相关者理论；三重底线理论；全方位社会责任管理；企业可持续发展能力</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
